Class MyQueue<E>

java.lang.Object
implementations.MyQueue<E>
Type Parameters:
E - the type of elements store in this queue
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, QueueADT<E>
public class MyQueue<E> extends Object implements QueueADT<E>
represents a queue data structure implemented using a doubly linked list
